Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.37,0:01:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个约定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水好清澈啊 好像镜子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.35,0:02:13.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好美的花儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.32,0:02:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 克拉拉 快点过来啊 这里有很少见的花儿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了 来了 这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能想海蒂那样走就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能用自己的双脚在这里散步 该会多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以的 克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定可以站起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是想要站起来也要费很大劲 而且还很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有刚开始才是这样子的 放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.24,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我下次来的时候\N你们可以两个一起爬山 你一定要好好努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天玩的很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.29,0:03:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢奶奶给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里 这是大家的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就在拉加兹温泉那里等你的好消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过奶奶也会偶尔到这里来看我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.81,0:03:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个嘛 我也想经常来看望你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过奶奶的身体啊……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 你们每天写信给我\N告诉我你们每天的进展吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都要写么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 短点也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 有什么事情我也能马上过来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.62,0:03:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 克拉拉\N我要是有不会写的字 你要教给我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.71,0:03:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写给奶奶的信可马虎不得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.32,0:03:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会每天给您写信的 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:04:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道什么时候会收到\N"克拉拉站起来了"这个好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.35,0:04:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.96,0:04:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想尽早站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:11.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会耐心等待的 克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老爷爷 她就拜托您照顾了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.74,0:04:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 约瑟夫 今天辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.67,0:04:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来\N彼得 今天多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.14,0:04:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天在村里办个晚会吧\N也算是给彼得今天带我们去湖边的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.95,0:04:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚会？\N对啊 送别晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以让彼得饱餐一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.57,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 有好消息哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么好消息啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是彼得你最喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.82,0:05:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是明天彼得可以……\N不行 克拉拉 现在不要告诉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？那是明天的惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊\N保密保密~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.26,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又保密啊 到底是什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.28,0:05:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事都没有啦\N明天傍晚到我们冬天住的家去就好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.11,0:05:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里有什么么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.09,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天实在是多谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与其让不认识的大叔抬着我 还是让彼得背我更开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.64,0:05:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点小事不用放在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.89,0:05:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天到底是……\N彼得今天辛苦了 多亏了你 大家玩的都很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.05,0:05:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 彼得\N明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.21,0:05:49.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶这就下山么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经让人等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明天也会早点下山的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙准备告别晚会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 你们和彼得一起过来就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不让我帮忙么？\N为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.99,0:06:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你们要给彼得一个惊喜是一个道理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要给你们一个惊喜 好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我知道了 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天你们一定会玩的很开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了\N哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N晚安 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.39,0:06:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.98,0:06:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶说是要给我们一个惊喜 到底会是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:06:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.57,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉\N哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶能留在拉加兹温泉 实在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩\N不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:19.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.54,0:07:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶留在拉加兹温泉是因为她相信我的双脚可以治好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.74,0:07:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.81,0:07:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是治不好的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.67,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 原来在担心这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以治好的 你都站起来过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是不能治好的话 你一次也站不来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的就是克拉拉的努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂\N嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的认为我的双脚可以治好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 一定可以治好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂\N克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么 我真的可以有这个希望么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.47,0:08:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 一起上山放牧 然后一起下山就好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 今天不要上山了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跑来跑去的 克拉拉的身体会受不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且明天开始 克拉拉就要做走路的练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走路的练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 一步一步的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.72,0:09:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始练习了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 不练习的话是站不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大将军 今天早点下来 然后我们一起下山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 这样好 傍晚见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:30.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷 明天要怎么练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,循序渐进的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 要开始练习走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.34,0:09:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂\N什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习了就能站起来走路么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为克拉拉一直都没有站起来走过路啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以得一点一点的来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩儿都是一点一点练习才能站起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.24,0:10:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我和小孩子是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 克拉拉已经站起来过了 经过练习 一定可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.05,0:10:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.57,0:10:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 疼不疼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.43,0:10:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:46.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 这次疼么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.46,0:10:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不疼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不要站起来看看?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 试试看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我站不起来 我站不起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再加把劲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.77,0:11:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.35,0:11:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 刚刚那么勉强你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.09,0:11:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我还是站不起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有的事 是我的方法不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我好好休息一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.05,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 我去给你拿杯羊奶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.58,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的能站起来么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 要不要再试一次？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我会更好的帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就算了吧 爷爷说了一会要下山的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒也是\N不说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 今天的晚会 你猜到了奶奶会做什么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.91,0:12:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有 绞尽脑汁也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉猜到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊 好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.18,0:12:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳还那么高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.26,0:12:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傍晚快点到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天时间过的真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.12,0:13:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干等着也不是办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.51,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带阿白去找药草吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.88,0:13:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 回来的好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不晚呢 我这已经是提前下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 小吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿白 黑熊 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.77,0:14:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天你们要看家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.98,0:14:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 是要下山吧\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下来的挺早啊 大将军\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.30,0:14:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里就拜托你们啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.27,0:14:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.58,0:14:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼得 今天回来的很早嘛\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.05,0:14:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎下山 彼得\N我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大婶好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海蒂 这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 今天一定又是有什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了? 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具体怎么回事我也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.52,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德国来的那个老婆婆从曼菲尔特请来不少人 可热闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.71,0:15:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也叫我过去做客了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.65,0:15:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫你过去？\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 剩下的交给我了 人家都请你过去了 快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.04,0:15:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么？那就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连彼得都被请去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开晚会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.13,0:15:58.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 彼得 快点 快点来看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是灯笼 好多灯笼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.38,0:16:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊 好像是白天一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的正是时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.71,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 请奏迎宾的音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.90,0:16:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家请入座吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们过去吧 爷爷\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.77,0:17:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢招待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪 这里可是爷爷的家哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 那些是我的朋友 请他们进来看看可以吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.44,0:17:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 大家一起来用餐吧 食物有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 大伙快过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,累了吧 克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事 谢谢爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊 我好喜欢 谢谢你 奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 克拉拉 我给你们介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.14,0:17:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那边开始 安娜莉 丽智 艾瑞克\N那位是科特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.49,0:17:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是学校里最小的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.02,0:18:04.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了这么多朋友 得把食物准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂娜 椅子和餐具就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 海蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.58,0:18:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了\N哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捉迷藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.39,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海蒂当鬼了 海蒂当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.98,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.73,0:19:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.59,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼小鬼 我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼小鬼 我们在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.63,0:19:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耍赖 跑到那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要跑 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.75,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该我当鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.72,0:19:35.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 要不要去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.13,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？\N恩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热闹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.74,0:19:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.05,0:20:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了 他们都跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要下去？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用 在这里就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:29.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样 大家玩的很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉也想要和大家一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 不过……
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你打心底里想要站起来 走起来 努力练习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定可以治好你的脚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是真的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.22,0:20:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不习惯是一定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许不会那么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许会很痛苦 也许不能马上就能站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这样也不能放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉现在最需要的就坚持不懈的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决心？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就开始做站起来的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.49,0:21:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.17,0:21:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.27,0:21:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们 开饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美味的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽情吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:47.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.72,0:22:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.50,0:22:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克拉拉 我会等待你的好消息的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.77,0:22:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恩 我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.31,0:22:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好消息赶快通知我哦 再见了 克拉拉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.12,0:22:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 海蒂 彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 奶奶\N再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.11,0:23:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶奶 我一定能站起来的 到时候会写信通知您的
